videos.description: Keyontae Johnson catches and nails a 3-pointer at halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Florida's Johnson hits 3 at halftime buzzer

videos.description: Tyson Carter splashes in a deep 3-pointer in front of his clapping father in the crowd.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Carter cans deep 3 and his father loves it

videos.description: Abdul Ado throws down a one-handed slam on the first shot of the game for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Ado opens scoring with a dunk

videos.description: Keyontae Johnson flies in and hammers down a vicious dunk.
videos.headline: Florida's Johnson flies in with a hammer

videos.description: Florida's Noah Locke evens the score with under a minute left after a Mississippi State player throws the ball back inbounds.
videos.headline: Florida ties it late after Mississippi State blunder

videos.description: Quinndary Weatherspoon runs past Florida defenders and knocks in the game-winning layup through contact to give Mississippi State 71-68 win.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Weatherspoon glides down the lane for GW layup
